'''尼克·桑多'''（'''Nick Sandow'''，{{bd|1966年|8月3日}}）是一名美國演員、編劇、監製和導演，最著名於《[[勁爆女子監獄|勁爆女子監獄]]》中飾演Joe Caputo。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/camila-gibran/the-wannabe-nick-sandows-farewell-to-old-new-york_b_7129750.html |title = 'The Wannabe': Nick Sandow's Farewell to Old New York |author = Camila Gibran |date = 2015-06-23 |publisher = The Huffington Post |language = en |accessdate = 2016-10-26 |archive-date = 2016-07-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160715193706/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/camila-gibran/the-wannabe-nick-sandows-farewell-to-old-new-york_b_7129750.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 早年 ==
桑多在[[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]的{{link-en|範尼斯特|Van Nest, Bronx}}成長。他在大約19歲時遷移至曼克頓，在兩年的專業演員培訓計劃中跟隨{{link-en|威廉·埃斯柏工作室|William Esper Studio|威廉·埃斯柏}}學習演藝，並在劇院工作。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://nypost.com/2015/07/06/meet-the-warden-who-rules-the-roost-on-oitnb/ |title = Meet the warden who rules the roost on ‘OITNB’ |author = Eric Hegedus |date = 2015-07-06 |publisher = New York Post |language = en |accessdate = 2020-03-09 |archive-date = 2019-05-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190514203125/https://nypost.com/2015/07/06/meet-the-warden-who-rules-the-roost-on-oitnb/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

